pr_title: Dynamic notification of whether a component is implemented in iOS (GSOC 2023)
pr_body:
This is the PR for my GSoC 2023 project.
Proposal link : https://docs.google.com/document/d/1oFaH2ULEED19wcx4171plxiXtfctRgV0-FU4EkjEIz8/edit?usp=sharing

1.  Added a new Dropdown button that provides users with options to filter components based on the operating system (OS) compatibility.
2. Made several changes to address build issues that were identified.
